data.description: Gorgeous one-level living on a double lot in Asheboro Country Club Estates overlooking the course! Built by Barry Knight, this home features a split bedroom floor plan & boasts hardwoods in the living areas, tray ceilings, arched doorways, custom built-ins, open living floor plan! Large primary suite with walk in closet, double vanities, soaking tub and separate shower! The kitchen offers great counter space, granite tops, and stainless appliances with a double oven. Mudroom/laundry room off the THREE CAR GARAGE is spacious! Huge bonus room-37 feet deep. Amazing outdoor spaces to savor the stunning natural views: private screened porch overlooking golf course, and outdoor stone fireplace with built-in sitting area &  an adjacent hot-tub area with live edge cedar accents. Hot tub is newer and remains. Located on a very private street in the cul-de-sac! Great walk-in crawlspace offers a tons of storage. Connecting lot is surveyed and buildable. This home is perfect for ANY stage of life!
